        BanUser constructor which takes UUIDs to create the object.
        Parameters:
        id - a UUID which stores the id of the user to kick
        banStart - a Date which indicates the start time of the ban
        banEnd - a Date which indicates the end time of the ban
        banner - a UUID which stores the id of the user who is issuing the ban
        reason - a String which stores a human readable reason as to why the user is being banned
